data.description: Conveniently located in Forest Bay Estates, this Rhett floor plan features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, 9' ceilings, a 2 car garage, and a fenced back yard. Kitchen features include granite countertops, SS appliances, bar area, and opens up to the dining area and family room for an open concept.  Primary Suite contains granite counters, dual vanities, garden tub, separate shower and walk in closet. Forest Bay Estates has a community pool, and is centrally located to with easy access to restaurants, shopping and many of the local beaches.
